    "body": "Not sure if this is the best way to do it but you could inspect your DOM and hide the first parent using javascript.\r\n\r\nSomething like this in jQuery\r\n$(\".ais-refinement-list--header\").css(\"display\", \"none\");\r\n\r\nInstead of ais-refinement-list--header, you would replace it with the class assigned to the first parent.",
